column5: <>A very tired nurse walks into a bank, totally exhausted after an 18-hour shift.  Preparing to write a check, she pulls a rectal thermometer out of her purse and tries to write with it.  When she realizes her mistake, she looks at the flabbergasted teller, and without missing a beat, she says:  'Well, that's great...that's just great...Some   has  got my pen!'
ANYONE KNOW THE DIFF BETWEEN AN ORAL AND A RECTAL THERMOMETER???
